node.text: @inayah worked her ass off while pregnant. I told her to take time for herself and she did that too but still was locked in. I don’t know how we pulled this off but we damn sure did and it’s special!  To all the women out there who are raising families and working at the highest level, I salute you all!  #SideA

node.title: Super woman is how I describe her

A huge thank you to our partners @empire @ghazi @nima_empire @tina.davis @oraclebfisher @molandy @pkflash97 also to my guy @skamartist we just getting started!  To my team @cithepluglicist @prmari @kelleykris_pr @lymelitemedia @getengaged @alexdermer @camfordham @benhiott @solomonpuryear and every dj, PD, MD, and editor that has supported and continues to do so. THANK YOU!

#CSHManagementGroup 
#Gold
